  "texts": [
    "It allows students to gain practical skills, understand industry challenges, and become better prepared for the dynamic and evolving cybersecurity landscape.",
    "An industry component in teaching cybersecurity would enhance the learning experience of students, especially if workshops featuring industry experts are organized as part of the curriculum, as highlighted by Hölbl and Welzer (2017).",
    "The work in Hölbl and Welzer (2017) is interesting as it also resulted in high student satisfaction.",
    "In some programmes such as those mentioned by Ahmed et al. (2022), capstone projects are sources of industry, which improves both the learning of students and the knowledge of industrial practices.",
    "The work in Yankson et al. (2024) underscored the imperative of industry-academia partnerships in fortifying cybersecurity training and awareness to combat the pervasive threat of cybercrime."
  ],
